00:28.747 --> 00:30.107
Daddy?

00:38.340 --> 00:39.980
'Edward?'

00:41.500 --> 00:43.539
'Edward?'

00:43.540 --> 00:45.340
A-A-A-A-A-Argh!

00:45.953 --> 00:48.233
Yargh!

00:50.573 --> 00:53.572
Eddie! Eddie! Wake up!

00:53.573 --> 00:55.533
Eddie, wake up!

00:56.793 --> 00:58.513
You were dreaming!

01:00.153 --> 01:01.593
I'm sorry.

01:02.673 --> 01:05.111
It's all right.

01:05.113 --> 01:07.112
You're home now. You're safe.

01:07.113 --> 01:08.553
'Jia-Li?!'

01:11.593 --> 01:13.193
Go to your room.

01:22.433 --> 01:24.472
Stay away from her.

01:24.473 --> 01:25.953
Or you'll regret it, boy.

01:48.047 --> 02:00.634
